    "As shown in Table 1, the prompt for creating a tutor chatbot comprised steps aligned with the multiple levels of PL.",
    "All participants signed informed consent forms before the experiment began.",
    "The participants attended a lecture that presented concepts and examples of education reform on the global stage.",
    "Following that, the participants were asked individually to initiate a session with the tutor bot.",
    "The intention of this activity is to have the tutor bot assume a pivotal role as a tutor, actively supporting the students by improving their answers, presenting pertinent examples, and guiding them to complete the tasks throughout their learning process."
